{"type": "article", "id": 28256, "title": "火箭咖啡桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-16T06:40:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702172907W39pBGfrL8ajMRJH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>童年意味着有大段无忧无虑的时间供我们幻想，最近来自塞浦路斯的家具设计师 <a href=\"http://www.mousarris.com/\">Stelios Mousarris</a> 就设计了一款火箭咖啡桌，把卡通似的机尾云和火箭从玩具收藏带到了现实生活当中，看起来既怀旧又富有童趣。火箭造型的桌腿并没有与玻璃桌面固定在一起，意味着你可以根据自己的喜好把它们摆放在不同的位置。制作过程结合了包括 3D 打印、树脂浇铸以及传统手工雕刻在内的各种不同的技术，<a href=\"http://www.mousarris.com/#!rocket-coffee-table/c1n22\">定制</a>价格为 5000 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172905NmvcHhF26LyYsTn9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172905mJ9KElfCNitDYo26.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172906dM8f19pjBKobqxs5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021729067hGnMItryxJ0jFeR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}